song.title: Swinth 1 Stationary Ark
song.info: Comments for subsong #1 TITLE: Stationary Ark ARTIST: John Mills-Cockell <?> COMMENT: "Theme from Stationary Ark, a nature show on PBS. [...] It appears on Synth Sample as interpreted by a friend of mine. I didn't know what it was myself until I happened to see Stationary Ark one time. This song does not play properly on some C-64's where the SID chip filter is calibrated differently." (GF)
